First I built a list of files
FileList=dir -recurse C:\temp\folderx -Attributes !Directory | ? name -notlike '*exe' | ? name -notlike '*dll'| select fullname  Then for each one, record the name to a log file, edit it and prompt for and store a comment
foreach ($F in $Filelist) { $F.Fullname &gt;&gt; commentlog.txt $File = $F.Fullname C:\Progra~2\vim\vim74\gvim.exe $File $Comment = read-host &quot;Changes made to $File&quot; $comment &gt;&gt; commentlog.txt }

